HVB Aims to Add More to UniCredit Earnings, Handelsblatt Says

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-06-02T14:24:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-02/hvb-aims-to-add-more-to-unicredit-earnings-handelsblatt-says.html
UniCredit SpA (UCG) ’s Hypovereinsbank unit
wants to contribute at least 50 percent of the bank’s earnings
in the coming years,  Handelsblatt reported , citing an interview
with Theodor Weimer, head of the unit.  The German unit plans to report pretax profit of more than
100 million euros ($144.5 million) in the retail business as
soon as possible, the newspaper said, citing Weimer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
